                        <interp inst="t18510303-name-244" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL RICH</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman,</hi> 615.) I took the prisoner, and found two shillings under his tongue.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoners Defence.</hi> I am innocent; I never thought of doing such a thing; I was going home at the time.</p>
